    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people say things like that to be nice but it feels so fake. it doesnt change the fact that i am just occupying space. like, if i just stopped trying to be seen, if i just drifted away, it wouldnt even be a tragedy. it would just be quiet. wouldnt a little more silence in the world be better than all this noise and pretending?",
